HSPC Practice Affiliation Type

A set of codes that describe how a provider is affiliated with an organization pertaining to the practice of medicine.

This value set includes codes from the following code systems:

  • Include all codes defined in http://hl7.org/fhir/practitioner-hspc-practiceAffiliationType
